  "summary": {
    "as": "Introduced", 
    "date": "1999-05-26", 
    "text": "Domestic Energy Production Security and Stabilization Act - Amends the Internal Revenue Code to set forth provisions relating to domestic oil and gas production which, among other things: (1) establish a credit for producing oil and gas from marginal wells; (2) make the depreciation adjustment inapplicable to oil and gas assets; and (3) permit a taxpayer to expense geological and geophysical expenditures and to delay rental payments in connection with oil and gas development."
